just about technology; it's about

44
00:02:29,106 --> 00:02:33,653
reducing client churn and attracting a
younger demographic of investors.<break

45
00:02:33,653 --> 00:02:34,480
time="0.5s" />

46
00:02:34,480 --> 00:02:38,718
Our goal is to replace their legacy
paper-based reporting with a real-time

47
00:02:38,718 --> 00:02:39,821
digital experience.

48
00:02:39,821 --> 00:02:43,843
Throughout this course, we'll document
the requirements for Polaris, navigating

49
00:02:43,843 --> 00:02:47,608
the conflicts between what the client
says they want and what the business

50
00:02:47,608 --> 00:02:49,980
actually needs to survive.<break
time="0.5s" />

51
00:02:49,980 --> 00:02:54,208
Before we begin, let’s take a quick look
at what topics we’ll cover in this

52
