We’ll also explore visual modeling,
contrast predictive Business Requirements

55
00:03:07,448 --> 00:03:11,774
Documents with adaptive Backlogs, and
finally, use the Traceability Matrix to

56
00:03:11,774 --> 00:03:15,929
ensure every deliverable aligns with a
business need.<break time="0.5s" />

57
